#EXTM3U
# ============================================================================
#  SabiStream — combined demo playlist  (Live TV + Movies + Series)   v3
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  Built for Google Play review / closed testing. Copyright-safe: Creative
#  Commons open movies (Blender Foundation — Big Buck Bunny & Sintel, CC BY 3.0,
#  www.blender.org) plus public developer test streams (Apple, Mux, Amazon
#  CloudFront). No paid TV, no broadcast/cable rebroadcast, no PPV, no sports.
#
#  WHAT CHANGED IN v3: the Movies and Series entries now play SOUND. v2 pointed
#  them at test-videos.co.uk, whose clips are encoded video-only (silent) — the
#  picture played but there was no audio track. All on-demand entries now use
#  the W3C HTML5 sample videos (media.w3.org), which carry a normal AAC audio
#  track, so movies and episodes play with sound. (v2 had already moved off
#  Google's old gtv-videos-bucket, which now returns AccessDenied on many
#  networks.) The Live section is unchanged.
#
#  HOW THE THREE TABS GET POPULATED  (SabiStream classifies a plain M3U by the
#  URL + name, NOT by the group name):
#    * Live TV - live HLS streams (.m3u8). group-title -> the Live category.
#    * Movies  - direct video files (.mp4) with no episode tag.
#                group-title -> the Movie category.
#    * Series  - .mp4 files whose NAME carries an episode tag like S01E01.
#                Episodes group by the show title (text BEFORE the SxxEyy token);
#                the season comes from the Sxx number.
# ============================================================================


# ------------------------------- LIVE TV ------------------------------------
